OL,6,FIt's been another who has been facing
OL,7,Fcriticism over donations received by
OL,8,Fhis leadership campaign from the owner
OL,9,Fof a company convicted of breaches of
OL,10,Fenvironmental law.
OL,12,FThere was further controversy over
OL,13,Fleaked text messages from a group of
OL,14,FLabour ministers which opponents
OL,15,Fclaimed showed that Mr Gething had
OL,16,Fdeleted covid-related conversations.
OL,17,FHe denied that the conversation was
OL,18,Fabout Welsh Government decision-making.
