OL,6,FHe told ITV Cymru Wales that
OL,7,F"Ministers need to be able to trust
OL,8,Feach other to share information fully
OL,9,Fand frankly and I hope that in the
OL,10,Ffuture there will be route back for
OL,11,FHannah to be able to come back to
OL,12,Fgovernment at some point."
OL,14,FHowever she posted a statement on
OL,15,Fsocial media saying that "I am deeply
OL,16,Fshocked and saddened by what has
OL,17,Fhappened today. I am clear and have
OL,18,Fbeen clear that I did not, nor have I
OL,19,Fever leaked anything. Integrity is all
OL,20,Fin politics and I retain mine."
