OL,6,FThen on Friday Plaid Cymru pulled out
OL,7,Fof its co-operation agreement with the
OL,8,FWelsh Government seven months before
OL,9,Fthe arrangement was due to end.
OL,11,FThe party's leader, Rhun ap Iorwerth
OL,12,Fsaid that, "I remain deeply concerned
OL,13,Fthat the First Minister has failed to
OL,14,Fpay back the #200,000 donation to his
OL,15,Fleadership campaign from a company
OL,16,Fconvicted of environmental offences,
OL,17,Fand believe it demonstrates a
OL,18,Fsignificant lack of judgement."
