OL,6,FHe added that, "I am worried by the
OL,7,Fcircumstances around the decision to
OL,8,Fsack a member of the Government this
OL,9,Fweek relating to matters that should
OL,10,Fbe in the public domain already."
OL,12,FThe difficult week ended with an
OL,13,Funusual Friday evening meeting of the
OL,14,FSenedd Labour group to discuss the
OL,15,Fsacking and Plaid Cymru's decision.
