OL,7,Fin their approaches and insisted that
OL,8,Fthey will continue to challenge the
OL,9,FFirst Minister.
OL,11,FWelsh Conservative leader Andrew RT
OL,12,FDavies told BBC Wales' Politics Wales
OL,13,Fprogramme that "It's about judgement
OL,14,Fon the donations. It's about
OL,15,Ftransparency on the WhatsApp messages,
OL,16,Fand its truthfulness when it comes to
OL,17,Fthe dismissal of the deputy minister
OL,18,Flast week. That's nothing to do with
