OL,8,FParty to deploy that line, when there
OL,9,Fare genuine cases of racism out there
OL,10,Fthat need to be tackled, and they
OL,11,Fshould be tackled head-on, for labour
OL,12,Fto deploy that line.
OL,14,F"This is about the confidence people
