OL,6,FVaughan Gething is likely to face
OL,7,Ffurther challenges from his political
OL,8,Fopponents in the Senedd this week but
OL,9,Fhe won't face a confidence vote
OL,10,Fdespite the Conservatives saying that
OL,11,Fthey'll look to hold one.
OL,13,FSenedd procedures mean a confidence
OL,14,Fmotion can't be brought this week and
OL,15,Fthe following week is a recess week.
OL,16,FThe earliest opportunity for such a
OL,17,Fvote is therefore Wednesday 5th June.
